话题就曾上过热搜。 当时有人发现，国内视频平台上1080P的清晰度还不如YouTube的720P，4K差距更是天差地别。 其实我们目前常见的分辨率表达方式是1080P、4K等，这些都只能片面的体现画面像素值，但并不能完全决定清晰度，而决定清晰度最重要的因素之一就是“码率”。 码率代表的是编码器每秒编出的数据大小，就类似游戏中的帧率数据，码率约稿就是帧率约稿，每秒画面越多，视频体积越大。 在同等分辨率下，码率越高，视频清晰度也就越高，而国内视频平台的清晰度差距主要就在这里。揭露平台降低码率等操作压缩画质！影视飓风新视频全网下架"},"attached_info":"CkAIq6ix6Ju70ZZSEAMaCTExMTAzODMzMyCxx5m4BjAAOMoBQAZyCTc5NDY5OTc1NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"81 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-5fd4f753bdf26ed02d6454f6ec4e6382_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"7_1728516474.295899","card_id":"Q_778191346","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":778191346,"title":"如果一个nba球星整个生涯都在一个弱队当大哥刷数据，他的历史地位能有多高？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/778191346","type":"question","created":1728356292,"answer_count":27,"follower_count":34,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[744,4196,35258,35704,52487],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"他有一线明星的水平，可以把各项数据刷的很高，但是球队每年都无缘季后赛或者首轮游，职业生涯从来没换过队，这样的球员退役后历史地位能有多高呢？"},"attached_info":"Cj8Iq6ix6Ju70ZZSEAMaCTExMTAwODMzNyDEv5K4BjAAOCJAB3IJNzc4MTkxMzQ2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"80 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-238e7224ef9d6d50552e9e51fa5b4056_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"8_1728516474.296258","card_id":"Q_797474474","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":797474474,"title":"国乒女团 1-3 爆冷不敌日本，遗憾获得2024 乒乓球亚锦赛女团亚军，如何评价双方的